  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink80-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">taṉṉai oḻiyap putuppuṉalāṭit tāḷttu vanta talaimakaṉōṭu talaimakaḷ pulantu
          colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink80">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>pulakkuvē mallēm poyyā turaimō</l>
          <l>nalattaku makaḷirkkut tōṭṭuṇai yākit</l>
          <l>talaippeyaṟ cempuṉa lāṭit</l>
          <l>tavanaṉi civantaṉa makiḻnaniṉ kaṇṇē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> We shall not sulk. [So] tell [us] without lying: </l>
          <p/>
          <l> Since bathing in the flood [made] red by the first rains, </l>
          <l> and befriending the shoulders of women of worthy beauty (OR women whom you value for
            their beauty?) </l>
          <l> your eyes have turned terribly red, o delightful man. </l>

        </lg>

      </div>
    </body>
